name: MONUMENTS 2021.09.23-00.15.55-1-2021.09.23-00.14.35
description:
The MONUMENTS series features generative illustrations of randomly crafted monumental buildings taking inspiration from different kind of iconic architectural features. Each piece is generated using a custom developed software, utilizing different mathematical random number generators.

Generative Illustration
Custom software (Javascript/Typescript + canvas-sketch)
Artist: Guido Schmidt
Year: 10/2021
